sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client (admin)
    participant Ctl as OrdersController
    participant Svc as PaymentPlan / Payments / Void service
    participant DB as Prisma / Postgres
    C->>Ctl: POST /:id/payment-plan/installments (confirm?)
    Ctl->>Svc: addInstallment(id, body, confirm)
    Svc->>DB: recheck Unallocated Balance in tx
    alt date warnings and not confirmed
        Svc-->>C: 200 OrderPaymentPlanChangePreviewDto (nothing written)
    else execute
        Svc->>DB: insert installment (copy Stripe identity if credit_card)
        Svc-->>C: 200 refreshed OrderPaymentPlanResponseDto
    end
    Note over C,Svc: PATCH …/:installment_id → exactly one of due_date | mark_as<br/>DELETE …/:installment_id → frees balance · POST …/void → terminal cancel-one
